Miss International Queen Vietnam 2018 is the first edition of Miss International Queen Vietnam pageant, was held on January 11, 2019 at Tân Bình Gymnasium, Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.
Persident of Miss International Queen Ms.Alisa Phanthusak crowned her successor Đỗ Nhật Hà of Ho Chi Minh City at the end of the event.
Nguyễn Hương Giang, Đoàn Di Băng, Dược Sĩ Tiến is a judge for the competition. Miss Supranational Vietnam 2016  and The Face Vietnam season 1  is a mentor for the competition.
